## üåê 4. Deploy to Streamlit Cloud (Free)

After pushing to GitHub:
1. Visit [streamlit.io/cloud](https://streamlit.io/cloud)
2. Click **"New app"**
3. Connect your GitHub repo
4. Set `ev_dashboard.py` as main file
5. Add secret or file settings if needed

It'll give you a link like:
https://electric-vehicle-specs-app-dyomtgw7tpebrghs9uqjvt.streamlit.app/

---

